Comment: 0,0:00:14.58,0:00:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Comment: 0,0:00:17.16,0:00:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro, did something happen?
Comment: 0,0:00:19.42,0:00:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it did.
Comment: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So something happened!
Comment: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened. Honestly, a lot happened.
Comment: 0,0:00:26.21,0:00:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So a lot happened?
Comment: 0,0:00:28.22,0:00:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:00:29.47,0:00:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Comment: 0,0:00:30.43,0:00:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, what?
Comment: 0,0:00:31.72,0:00:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just, it creeps me out to hear you answering so honestly.
Comment: 0,0:00:34.47,0:00:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Even if you were the one who asked?
Comment: 0,0:00:36.47,0:00:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, you never have a normal response to anything.
Comment: 0,0:00:39.27,0:00:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, true.
Comment: 0,0:00:40.94,0:00:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess.
Comment: 0,0:00:42.23,0:00:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Comment: 0,0:00:45.69,0:00:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask what happened?
Comment: 0,0:00:54.16,0:00:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you everything when it's all over.
Comment: 0,0:00:56.33,0:00:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, sure.
Comment: 0,0:00:57.95,0:01:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. That's how things are right now,
Comment: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,so all of us getting together to celebrate would feel kind of weird.
Comment: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright...
Comment: 0,0:01:05.59,0:01:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess we can't do anything about that, then.
Comment: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, worst case, I'll settle for just celebrating with you.
Comment: 0,0:01:12.05,0:01:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then.
Comment: 0,0:01:13.26,0:01:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, "worst case"?
Comment: 0,0:01:14.51,0:01:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I was thinking about surprising you with a little something when we celebrated,
Comment: 0,0:01:19.31,0:01:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,so this actually works out well!
Comment: 0,0:01:21.44,0:01:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it'd be embarrassing if anyone else saw it!
Comment: 0,0:01:24.77,0:01:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's this surprise about?
Comment: 0,0:01:26.61,0:01:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's touching, even if I know about it beforehand.
Comment: 0,0:01:28.65,0:01:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? That's gonna get me a lot of points!
Comment: 0,0:01:30.74,0:01:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,True.
Comment: 0,0:01:31.57,0:01:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's giving me a very high hurdle to jump. I hope I'll be able to give you a good surprise.
Comment: 0,0:01:36.58,0:01:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's have a quiet gathering with only family this time around.
Comment: 0,0:01:40.04,0:01:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you say that? Is this a funeral?
Comment: 0,0:01:41.91,0:01:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're totally making it sound like a memorial service...
Comment: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, shall we have breakfast?
Comment: 0,0:01:54.89,0:01:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagare kitta moji no ato
Comment: 0,0:03:24.56,0:03:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was thinking, since the soccer club is on break starting today,
Comment: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,before the school, we can go out with a bang and do karaoke or something like that!
Comment: 0,0:03:33.11,0:03:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And then like, for spring vacation we could maybe all plan a trip somewhere, yeah?
Comment: 0,0:03:38.49,0:03:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato, is there anywhere you wanna go?
Comment: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, for me, I'd totally be down for some sort of long trip somewhere.
Comment: 0,0:03:45.08,0:03:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Though if you wanna stay close, doing a BBQ at the seaside park is a great way to end our 2nd year of...
Comment: 0,0:03:48.71,0:03:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I...
Comment: 0,0:03:49.71,0:03:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:03:57.76,0:03:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Just talk to me like a normal person!
Comment: 0,0:04:02.39,0:04:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Speaking of, I heard the news from Yukinon yesterday.
Comment: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're having a prom, huh?
Comment: 0,0:04:07.52,0:04:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah... So you heard.
Comment: 0,0:04:09.94,0:04:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, last night. She sent me a LINE message. Then we met up and chatted for a bit.
Comment: 0,0:04:15.49,0:04:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Comment: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind if we stop here for a few?
Comment: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh crap!
Comment: 0,0:04:22.58,0:04:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't been on a swing in so long, it's kinda scary now!
Comment: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Much scarier than I thought!
Comment: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Comment: 0,0:04:28.25,0:04:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Comment: 0,0:04:40.47,0:04:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuigahama...
Comment: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me what your wish is.
Comment: 0,0:04:45.85,0:04:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Comment: 0,0:04:47.81,0:04:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me rephrase that.
Comment: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's anything you want me to do, or some wish I could grant, then please tell me.
Comment: 0,0:04:56.19,0:05:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot. Like, I want you to be more normal when you start conversations with me.
Comment: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And quit looking at me out of the corner of your eye.
Comment: 0,0:05:02.91,0:05:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, I want you to reply to my messages faster, and quit being so picky. And, also-
Comment: 0,0:05:09.29,0:05:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, my bad, sorry I was born, alright?
Comment: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But damn, hearing it all from you makes me sound like a really terrible guy. I'm downright creepy.
Comment: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just noticing that now?
Comment: 0,0:05:17.84,0:05:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The damange inflicted from hearing someone else say it is way worse than just thinking it myself.
Comment: 0,0:05:22.13,0:05:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you totally lambasted me with that long list of "wishes."
Comment: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I just feel like a punching bag.
Comment: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, I fully intend to try and improve on all of that stuff.
Comment: 0,0:05:29.81,0:05:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that's impossible, so just forget about it.
Comment: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,「あ、でも、今日みたいにいきなり予定決められちゃうのはちょっと直してほしいかも。暇なときは全然いいんだけど、準備したいなーってときもあるし」
Comment: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but it'd be nice if you could cut back on making plans at the last minute like you did today.
Comment: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's totally fine when I'm free, but occasionally I wish I had some time to prepare.
Comment: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right. I'm really sorry about that.
Comment: 0,0:05:45.58,0:05:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And also...
Comment: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still more? There's a lot of 'em, huh? I'm sorry for everything.
Comment: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No kidding!
Comment: 0,0:05:55.46,0:05:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How much easier things would be if I could just go on chatting with her like this?
Comment: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Not saying anything of importance, and pretending like things are totally normal.
Comment: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Purposely avoiding the heart of the matter...
Comment: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,However, allowing myself to do that would be the same as betraying myself.
Comment: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not really what I wanted to talk about.
Comment: 0,0:06:16.15,0:06:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what, then?
Comment: 0,0:06:17.36,0:06:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about that competition. The one where the loser has to do anything the winner says.
Comment: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The competition isn't over yet, is it?
Comment: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's true, but...
Comment: 0,0:06:25.74,0:06:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've already accepted defeat. And that means the competition is over.
Comment: 0,0:06:31.04,0:06:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You just decided that arbitrarily.
Comment: 0,0:06:33.79,0:06:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I've lost. In fact, I lost so badly it almost feels good.
Comment: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So let me grant your wish.
Comment: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a greedy person, so I can't choose just one thing...
Comment: 0,0:06:54.69,0:06:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Comment: 0,0:06:57.23,0:06:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it possible for you to grant all of my wishes?
Comment: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody asks the Genie that, huh?
Comment: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll do whatever I can that's within my ability.
Comment: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you should stop that.
Comment: 0,0:07:08.87,0:07:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikky, you're always like that. For things you can't do, you just say you'll do it within your ability.
Comment: 0,0:07:08.87,0:07:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,「ヒッキー、いつもそうじゃん。できないのに、できる範囲でって言って、それで、結局なんとかするの。すっごい無理して」
Comment: 0,0:07:14.71,0:07:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the end, you make it work, but by really pushing yourself.
Comment: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'll only ask you for simple things.
Comment: 0,0:07:22.55,0:07:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't exactly know what to wish for, but... there are things that I want to do.
Comment: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Like what?
Comment: 0,0:07:31.39,0:07:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,First off, I want to help Yukinon. I want to see prom through to the end.
Comment: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Comment: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, I want to throw a party for Komachi.
Comment: 0,0:07:38.90,0:07:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Comment: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And, I want to go hang out somewhere or something.
Comment: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Comment: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Comment: 0,0:07:49.66,0:07:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey, what do you want to do during vacation?
Comment: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... I think I wanna go have fun somewhere!
Comment: 0,0:07:53.62,0:07:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's do it!
Comment: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, really?!
Comment: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Comment: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to grant your wish, Hikky.
Comment: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I get a wish? Hard to choose...
Comment: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? So start thinking about what you want.
Comment: 0,0:08:09.43,0:08:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,While we're granting my other wishes, I'll think about what I want, too.
Comment: 0,0:08:16.52,0:08:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, I'll tell you.
Comment: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So please, let me hear yours.
Comment: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Comment: 0,0:08:34.16,0:08:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking?
Comment: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Comment: 0,0:08:36.83,0:08:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,About Yui.
Comment: 0,0:08:42.63,0:08:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I'm not really your friend or anything so I don't care, but that's not the case for Yui.
Comment: 0,0:08:49.30,0:08:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't be all half-assed about this, okay?
Comment: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd piss me off.
Comment: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best.
Comment: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it. Bye.
Comment: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a good person.
Comment: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikky! Yahallo!
Comment: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's freezing!
Comment: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyday's just freezing cold, huh?
Comment: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,When I woke up this morning, it was like... Oh...
Comment: 0,0:09:14.41,0:09:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Yukinon!
Comment: 0,0:09:15.91,0:09:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, sounds good.
Comment: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuigahama.
Comment: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so I see you were walking together.
Comment: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well. How are things?
Comment: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything going smoothly?
Comment: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, I'm not so sure. Right?
Comment: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,W-well, I would say...
Comment: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Launching an event requires logistics and logistics hardly ever go smoothly,
Comment: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but we aren't dealing with any major problems currently.
Comment: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's the gist of it.
Comment: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukinon, that was way too complicated! Explain it better!
Comment: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Comment: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Things aren't going well enough to say it's "smooth," so I was concerned how best to phrase it...
Comment: 0,0:09:49.36,0:09:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That was way too honest!
Comment: 0,0:09:51.74,0:09:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's very much like you, Yukinon.
Comment: 0,0:09:56.83,0:09:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's going okay.
Comment: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,As of right now, it's just kinda working out somehow.
Comment: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hard to say how it will utimately turn out, though.
Comment: 0,0:10:03.17,0:10:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing everything to make sure it doesn't fail.
Comment: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Which about sums it up.
Comment: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Well, don't push yourself.
Comment: 0,0:10:09.55,0:10:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh please, we're already pushing ourselves way too hard!
Comment: 0,0:10:11.80,0:10:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to or else we'll run out of time.
Comment: 0,0:10:13.68,0:10:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly though, we could really use some manpower.
Comment: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that today and tomorrow are going to be the most stressful due to the workload.
Comment: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But I believe we can handle it just fine without calling in more people to help.
Comment: 0,0:10:23.94,0:10:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And a large part of that is thanks to your efforts.
Comment: 0,0:10:28.11,0:10:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, today is a no go, but I can help you out starting tomorrow so let me know.
Comment: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?!
Comment: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Isshiki. Tomorrow's focus is on the technical rehearsal,
Comment: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,「一色さん、明日はテクリハが中心だから大きな作業は発生しないわ。だから、人が多い必要もないと思うけれど
Comment: 0,0:10:36.87,0:10:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,so there won't be any large-scale work going on.
Comment: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think there's any need for a large number of people.
Comment: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so? Um...
Comment: 0,0:10:45.50,0:10:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I'm not an interpreter for you two.
Comment: 0,0:10:55.26,0:10:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We should leave now. See you later.
Comment: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,'Kay, see ya.
Comment: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Help us on the day of prom, okay?
Comment: 0,0:11:06.48,0:11:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, I welcome you to show up any time!
Comment: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I will if I'm free.
Comment: 0,0:11:11.53,0:11:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always free, so just straight up say, "Okay, I'll help."
Comment: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a pain, ugh!
Comment: 0,0:11:17.66,0:11:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Comment: 0,0:11:20.33,0:11:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that things are going well for them.
Comment: 0,0:11:23.08,0:11:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Agreed.
Comment: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if things really are going well. Has she become able to better conduct herself?
Comment: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Giống như cách làm quen với khoảng thời gian đó.
Comment: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll probably get used to this relationship as well.
Comment: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikky.
Comment: 0,0:11:39.18,0:11:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you free?
Comment: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose so.
Comment: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Comment: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to come to my house on Saturday?
Comment: 0,0:11:45.52,0:11:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think I will.
Comment: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But you said you were free!
Comment: 0,0:11:48.23,0:11:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's true, I am free.
Comment: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We said we'd make a cake for Komachi, right? I thought we could do that.
Comment: 0,0:11:57.49,0:12:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. Well, if that's what we're doing... I'll come over.
Comment: 0,0:12:01.37,0:12:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Comment: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's perfect because my mom will be in the house that day to teach us stuff!
Comment: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Hikky, right?
Comment: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui has told me so much about you!
Comment: 0,0:12:10.71,0:12:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom! You really don't have to tell him that!
Comment: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want to talk to Hikky, too!
Comment: 0,0:12:17.05,0:12:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is gonna be awkward...
Comment: 0,0:12:19.34,0:12:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make tea so have a seat wherever!
Comment: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,S-sure...
Comment: 0,0:12:29.77,0:12:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:12:31.27,0:12:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought Gaha-mama was supposed to be here...
Comment: 0,0:12:34.78,0:12:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Comment: 0,0:12:35.32,0:12:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks.
Comment: 0,0:12:37.57,0:12:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Sable?
Comment: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom's taking him for a walk. I think they'll be home soon.
Comment: 0,0:12:42.45,0:12:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Comment: 0,0:12:47.33,0:12:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go ahead and ask...
Comment: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Comment: 0,0:12:50.25,0:12:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Where might your father be on this fine day?
Comment: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you say it like that? Creepy.
Comment: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess my dad's at work. Not sure though.
Comment: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we could make some cookies?
Comment: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, I don't like that idea.
Comment: 0,0:13:10.27,0:13:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's better to make something more impressive.
Comment: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for having me. And thank you for your help today.
Comment: 0,0:13:16.61,0:13:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me! I will do my best to-
Comment: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Mom... I'll call for you later so go away.
Comment: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you said you wanted my help!
Comment: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah and I'll come get you when your help is actually needed!
Comment: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I-it's okay, let her stay... she might have some good insight.
Comment: 0,0:13:29.54,0:13:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! It's better if you think about what to make with me around!
Comment: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, fine then.
Comment: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think is best, Mom?
Comment: 0,0:13:38.84,0:13:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you're making it especially from scratch, then you should choose something exquisite.
Comment: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Something exquisite...
Comment: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of sweets do you think would be good, Hikky?
Comment: 0,0:13:48.60,0:13:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,By "exquisite" I assume you mean...
Comment: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...something stylish and expensive looking that's suitable for posting on Instagram
Comment: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and can be used to brag to fellow moms.
Comment: 0,0:13:55.90,0:13:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch your mouth...
Comment: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You seriously came at it from a housewife's perspective?!
Comment: 0,0:14:00.24,0:14:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My recommendation is a fruit tart!
Comment: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, that one looks kinda difficult.
Comment: 0,0:14:05.91,0:14:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No joke.
Comment: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, just fine!
Comment: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We can just buy prepared tart crusts, so all that's needed is arranging the filling.
Comment: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy peasy!
Comment: 0,0:14:16.34,0:14:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Which fruits should we use?
Comment: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Peach!
Comment: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Peach season comes later. Summer is the right time for those.
Comment: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikky, what fruits do you like?
Comment: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You like peanuts, huh?
Comment: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you just answer for me?
Comment: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, she said fruits. FRUITS. We're talking about fruits right now.
Comment: 0,0:14:33.48,0:14:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Đang nói về trái cây nhé!
Comment: 0,0:14:34.85,0:14:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If I have to choose, I like pears.
Comment: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The pears from Chiba are the best in Japan; actually, the world!
Comment: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are a Chiba boy!
Comment: 0,0:14:42.24,0:14:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But pears aren't in season right now, either. Well, if we want peaches, we can use canned ones.
Comment: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Canned peaches...
Comment: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you wanna do, Hikky?
Comment: 0,0:14:50.87,0:14:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter to me. Komachi's not particularly picky, either. I guess peach would be good.
Comment: 0,0:14:56.71,0:14:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,However, if we're using canned peaches, the time of year or whatever doesn't matter, right?
Comment: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be the truth right now.
Comment: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But the season will still come.
Comment: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Many years will pass, and when you eat a peach as a grown up,
Comment: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll remember this sort of thing happened, you know?
Comment: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what's so wonderful about homemade sweets.
Comment: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds really nice!
Comment: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Comment: 0,0:15:19.61,0:15:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's really effective for attracting boys!
Comment: 0,0:15:21.61,0:15:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You ruined it! Now it sounds manipulative!
Comment: 0,0:15:27.20,0:15:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get started now.
Comment: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I think this has gotta be delicious with some chocolate on it!
Comment: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, wait...
Comment: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Hikky!
Comment: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it good?
Comment: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the sorts of things you should test out on yourself first.
Comment: 0,0:15:58.27,0:16:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I thought for sure it would be yummy...
Comment: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to use chocolate...
Comment: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, so you can coat the crust with it...
Comment: 0,0:16:08.66,0:16:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, say, "Aah!"
Comment: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-thank you.
Comment: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do it.
Comment: 0,0:16:15.83,0:16:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious, too delicious.
Comment: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Comment: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, here. You next, Yui. Say, "Aah!"
Comment: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it really is good!
Comment: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Mom?
Comment: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, tastes good to me. Now we add the secret ingredient, and it'll be all done.
Comment: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Secret ingredient?
Comment: 0,0:16:36.98,0:16:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, it's the ultimate flavoring...
Comment: 0,0:16:39.48,0:16:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mumble, mumble, mumble...
Comment: 0,0:16:41.98,0:16:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez! If you're going to say things like that you can go away!
Comment: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Comment: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hikky, what do you think the secret ingredient is?
Comment: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, what could it be?
Comment: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose it's "hunger" or something?
Comment: 0,0:16:57.37,0:17:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me guess. The fact that it comes out of somebody else's pocket.
Comment: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Food tastes better that way.
Comment: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikky, that's kind of despicable.
Comment: 0,0:17:03.34,0:17:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Think more about the fact that it's homemade.
Comment: 0,0:17:10.26,0:17:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be devotion, then.
Comment: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for today.
Comment: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be the one thanking you.
Comment: 0,0:17:27.28,0:17:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But I did have fun.
Comment: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great making things together. It's fun.
Comment: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing the work alone is more efficient, though.
Comment: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Comment: 0,0:17:39.33,0:17:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Having tried my hand at cooking, I gotta admit...
Comment: 0,0:17:42.25,0:17:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't feel like work at all. Making things together really is fun.
Comment: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Komachi might enjoy that, too. She really loves doing house work and stuff.
Comment: 0,0:17:54.47,0:17:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... It might be good to make things together then!
Comment: 0,0:17:57.97,0:17:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So... here's this.
Comment: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Your cookies were delicious.
Comment: 0,0:18:18.58,0:18:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is like a thank you for them. Kinda early, but...
Comment: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The ingredients are the same as the ones we ate earlier, right?
Comment: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not quite true.
Comment: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I covertly added a secret ingredient.
Comment: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... What did you put in it?
Comment: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Telling you wouldn't make it much of a secret, would it?
Comment: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...I guess not.
Comment: 0,0:18:42.77,0:18:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I could continue living out my days like this, granting all of her wishes one by one.
Comment: 0,0:18:48.86,0:18:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That impossible fantasy played out in my head.
Comment: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Last but not least, I humbly pray for the health and success of all the graduates
Comment: 0,0:18:56.49,0:19:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and offer my sincerest farewell as the representative of the student body.
Comment: 0,0:19:02.08,0:19:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Student Body Representative, Iroha Isshiki.
Comment: 0,0:19:10.63,0:19:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, a representative of the graduating class will offer their own speech.
Comment: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, as the warm rays of the sun shine on...
Comment: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And, in terms of my own high school life, the most precious experiences that I had were all...
Comment: 0,0:19:39.87,0:19:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,as a member of the student council.
Comment: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There were many events that we worked together as a school to put on.
Comment: 0,0:19:46.54,0:19:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The most memorable events were the culture festival and the sports festival.
Comment: 0,0:19:50.67,0:19:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They were a real handful!
Comment: 0,0:19:54.34,0:19:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take this!
Comment: 0,0:19:58.47,0:19:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachiman, are you okay?
Comment: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Tank yew...
Comment: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Bể thủy tùng...
Comment: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit being such a faucet.
Comment: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikitani, do you have hay fever? It's gotta be the pollen, yeah? I totally know your pain!
Comment: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I got hay fever too, and it always gets so crappy right before spring hits!
Comment: 0,0:20:10.19,0:20:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Tobe, quiet down!
Comment: 0,0:20:11.86,0:20:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Comment: 0,0:20:11.86,0:20:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Lấy làm tiếc.
Comment: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I extend a word of thanks to all of you, as representative of the graduating class.
Comment: 0,0:20:21.07,0:20:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, everyone! I had so much fun! It was amazing!
Comment: 0,0:20:28.46,0:20:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all culture-ing?!
Comment: 0,0:20:37.09,0:20:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiba's Specialties!
Comment: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Dance and Festivals!
Comment: 0,0:20:41.14,0:20:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,When in Rome...
Comment: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...dance like the Romans!
Comment: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sing a Song!
Comment: 0,0:21:02.20,0:21:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimi no yokogao ga
Comment: 0,0:00:01.98,0:00:03.98,ED-Kanji-Yukino,ED,0,0,0,,ED
Comment: 0,0:00:05.99,0:00:07.99,ED-Kanji-Yukino,ED-Kanji,0,0,0,,ED-Kanji
Comment: 0,0:22:08.27,0:22:10.27,ED-Kanji-Both,ED-Vie,0,0,0,,Ed-Vie
