Comment: 0,0:01:16.06,0:01:18.06,ED-Kanji-Both,ED,0,0,0,,ED
Comment: 0,0:22:18.65,0:22:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Man... I never thought I'd actually graduate...
Comment: 0,0:22:23.99,0:22:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but I knew all along! I fully intended to graduate! And I'm totally going to university!
Comment: 0,0:22:29.83,0:22:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But, that's not what I mean... it's like... it's like... like something else!
Comment: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you mean.
Comment: 0,0:22:38.38,0:22:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You all gotta go out and do something fun again!
Comment: 0,0:22:41.92,0:22:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already graduated, though.
Comment: 0,0:22:45.89,0:22:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But you, and Hikigaya, and the others still have time for that.
Comment: 0,0:22:49.35,0:22:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Comment: 0,0:22:50.22,0:22:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do everything we can.
Comment: 0,0:22:51.64,0:22:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, great! I'm done with my farewells!
Comment: 0,0:22:56.65,0:23:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, I'll see you guys later! Let's talk a lot at prom, 'kay?
Comment: 0,0:23:04.40,0:23:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you really like Meguri, don't you?
Comment: 0,0:23:08.33,0:23:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I thought that, too!
Comment: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Are there people that DON'T like her?
Comment: 0,0:23:12.83,0:23:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... I don't think so.
Comment: 0,0:23:14.50,0:23:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And why do you sound so angry?
Comment: 0,0:23:18.54,0:23:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Irohas? Don't make that "Uh, of course there are..." face at me!
Comment: 0,0:23:23.30,0:23:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why people don't like you!
Comment: 0,0:23:24.38,0:23:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then for the sake of your beloved Meguri, I've got a little job for you to throw your back into!
Comment: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The way she words things just stings!
Comment: 0,0:23:35.64,0:23:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, that graduation ceremony was so amazing! Maybe the best ever!
Comment: 0,0:23:39.06,0:23:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta write some sort of poetic recap to post on social media when I get home.
Comment: 0,0:23:41.78,0:23:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Hikky, you were bawling your eyes out.
Comment: 0,0:23:44.03,0:23:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well yeah, because I've got the powers of the emo-emo fruit. I turn emo at the drop of a hat.
Comment: 0,0:23:47.66,0:23:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But c'mon, anybody would cry at that ceremony!
Comment: 0,0:23:49.53,0:23:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Listening to Isshiki's speech made me realize that
Comment: 0,0:23:51.91,0:23:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,even she put some real effort in, as hopeless as she is.
Comment: 0,0:23:53.62,0:23:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But Meguri totally stole the show!
Comment: 0,0:23:54.91,0:23:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She put on a brave face at first, but then the tears came, and her smile after that was priceless!
Comment: 0,0:23:58.58,0:24:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the call and response at the end, she must've totally adlibbed that!
Comment: 0,0:24:01.04,0:24:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, hold on, I think I might cry again.
Comment: 0,0:24:01.80,0:24:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking way too much!
Comment: 0,0:24:02.80,0:24:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ew, gross, scary. I'm out.
